Privacy Policy
Your privacy and data security are our top priorities

Introduction
Welcome to our Astroz Development! We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we use it, and the measures we take to safeguard your data while using our bot's features.

Information Collection
User Information
This includes Discord usernames, user IDs, and server IDs to provide personalized features and manage server-specific settings.

Message Content
Messages sent to or via the bot may be temporarily stored to provide functionalities such as moderation, automoderation, and autoresponder services.

Server Data
Information about your server configuration, such as roles, permissions, and channel structures, to enable features like reaction roles, verification, and utility commands.

Usage of Information
Feature Provision
To deliver and enhance features such as the economy system, games, giveaways, fun activities, and more.

Moderation and Security
To maintain server security, enforce rules, and prevent unauthorized changes or malicious attacks.

User Engagement
To personalize user experiences, manage role assignments, and provide automated responses to common queries.

Data Storage and Security
Data Retention
We retain collected data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy. Temporary data, such as message content, is stored only for the duration needed to provide the relevant feature.

Security Measures
We employ encryption, access controls, and regular security audits to ensure the safety of your information.

Third-Party Services
Our bot may integrate with third-party services to enhance its functionality. We ensure that any third-party service providers comply with relevant data protection regulations and handle your data securely.

User Rights
You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information at any time. If you have any concerns about your data or need assistance, please contact us through the support channels provided.

Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. Any updates will be communicated through our Discord server or other appropriate channels.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please reach out to us via our support system.

Questions About Privacy?
If you have any concerns about your data or need clarification on our privacy practices, we're here to help.

Contact Support at discord.gg/shadow-x or discord.gg/astrozdev
